String pOSub =
    'Programme outcomes serve as guides for curriculum development, development of teaching methodologies and assessment strategies, skills programme and depth of industrial exposure and collaborations required to produce graduates in the required discipline. The programme Objectives of Bachelor of Engineering (B.Eng./B.Sc.) in Systems Engineering are woven around the University of Lagos and the Department of Systems Engineering visions and missions and contain the knowledge, skills and attributes expected of graduates of Systems Engineering to possess in consonance with the mantra of excellence in learning and research and of the University of Lagos.';
